{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/memasang-LAMP-stack-ubuntu-bionic/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>LAMP merupakan sebuah singkatan untuk Linux, Apache, Mariadb(atau Mysql), dan PHP. LAMP merupakan kombinasi yang paling sering dipakai untuk membangun web server sederhana di sistem operasi berbasis GNU/Linux. Biasanya untuk mempermudah penngaturan database ditambahkan phpMyAdmin, utillity tambahan yang berguna untuk memudahkan manajemen database mariadb.</p>\n<h3>Memasang Apache</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> apache2</code></pre></div>\n<p>Buka <a href=\"http://localhost/\">http://localhost/</a> dibrowser untuk melihat apakah apache2 sukses terpasang.</p>\n<h3>Mengaktifkan ufw</h3>\n<p>ufw merupakan simple firewall yang tersedia secara default di Ubuntu</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> ufw <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">enable</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> ufw status</code></pre></div>\n<p>Mengizinkan apache di ufw</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> ufw allow <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Apache Full\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Memasang gufw</h3>\n<p>gufw merupakan ufw berbasis GUI untuk memudahkan pengaturan ufw yang berbasis cli.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gufw</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Memasang dan konfigurasi Mariadb</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> mariadb-server mariadb-client\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> mysql_secure_installation</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/ad00e/ssmariadb.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot mysql_secure_installation\"\n        title=\"Screenshot mysql_secure_installation\"\n        src=\"/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/5a190/ssmariadb.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/772e8/ssmariadb.png 200w,\n/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/e17e5/ssmariadb.png 400w,\n/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/5a190/ssmariadb.png 800w,\n/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/c1b63/ssmariadb.png 1200w,\n/static/ab77bb3051709a916c8b45a811f11f62/ad00e/ssmariadb.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nTekan enter dua kali. Masukkan password lalu tekan enter. Masukkan password lagi dan tekan enter. Selanjutnya tekan enter terus hingga <code class=\"language-text\">mysql_secure_installation</code> keluar.</p>\n<h3>Memasang PHP</h3>\n<p>PHP yang tersedia di repository Ubuntu Bionic ialah versi 5.6 dan 7.2 untuk memasang versi 7.2 masukkan perintah :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> php php-common php-mysql php-gd php-cli</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Memasang phpMyAdmin dan konfigurasi</h3>\n<p>Masukkan perintah : </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> phpmyadmin</code></pre></div>\n<p>Saat muncul opsi diminta memilih tekan tombol space dan tekan enter.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/ad00e/ssphpma.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot pemasangan phpMyAdmin\"\n        title=\"Screenshot pemasangan phpMyAdmin\"\n        src=\"/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/5a190/ssphpma.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/772e8/ssphpma.png 200w,\n/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/e17e5/ssphpma.png 400w,\n/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/5a190/ssphpma.png 800w,\n/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/c1b63/ssphpma.png 1200w,\n/static/0ade4dd9d7825a7790adcb0d58c586c2/ad00e/ssphpma.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Tekan enter jika muncul permintaan untuk memilih atau mengisi password.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/ad00e/ssphpma2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot pemasangan phpMyAdmin\"\n        title=\"Screenshot pemasangan phpMyAdmin\"\n        src=\"/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/5a190/ssphpma2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/772e8/ssphpma2.png 200w,\n/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/e17e5/ssphpma2.png 400w,\n/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/5a190/ssphpma2.png 800w,\n/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/c1b63/ssphpma2.png 1200w,\n/static/b0767d13e592a54b14f244fd15917fef/ad00e/ssphpma2.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Selanjutnya konfigurasi akun untuk phpMyAdmin</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> mysql -u root -p</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">USER</span> <span class=\"token string\">'admin'</span><span class=\"token variable\">@'localhost'</span> IDENTIFIED <span class=\"token keyword\">BY</span> <span class=\"token string\">'password'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">GRANT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ALL</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">PRIVILEGES</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TO</span> <span class=\"token string\">'admin'</span><span class=\"token variable\">@'localhost'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">GRANT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">OPTION</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nFLUSH <span class=\"token keyword\">PRIVILEGES</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\\q</code></pre></div>\n<p>Buka <a href=\"http://localhost/phpmyadmin\">http://localhost/phpmyadmin</a> untuk mengakses phpMyAdmin dengan username \"admin\" dan password \"password\".</p>\n<p>Selesai, LAMP Stack telah terinstall beserta dengan phpMyAdmin. Directory root untuk LAMP Stack ini berada pada <code class=\"language-text\">/var/www/html</code>.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Memasang LAMP Stack di Ubuntu 18.04 Bionic Beaver beserta phpMyAdmin"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/memasang-LAMP-stack-ubuntu-bionic/"}}}